org.enquery.encryptedquery.responder.wideskies.common

Class HashSelectorAndPartitionData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.enquery.encryptedquery.responder.wideskies.common.HashSelectorAndPartitionData

  • public class HashSelectorAndPartitionData
extends java.lang.Object
    Given a MapWritable or JSON formatted dataElement, this class gives the common functionality to extract the selector by queryType from each dataElement, perform a keyed hash of the selector, extract the partitions of the dataElement, and outputs <hash(selector), dataPartitions>
